title: Daenerys Targaryen
body:
This yarn is inspired by Daenerys of House Targaryen from Game of Thrones.

 This yarn is available on:

Honey Fingering: Fingering/3 Ply, 100% Superwash Merino. 100g/448m/490yds

Luxury Sock: 80/10/10 SW Merino/Cashmere/Nylon 100g/350m/382yds

Sparkle Sock - Gold: 75/20/5 SW Merino/Nylon/Stellina. 100g/400m/437yds

All Yarns are hand painted and kettle dyed. This means that every yarn can vary. If you need multiple yarns for a project, it is highly recommended that you purchase them at the same time so that they can come from the same dye lot. Some of the brighter colors can bleed, even though they have been rinsed multiple times, if you notice this run under cold water until water is clear.

Care: Hand wash in cold water and lay flat to dry

All products are created in a smoke free and pet friendly environment. 

All photographs are used as inspiration for the yarn and are not owned by myself and belong to the franchise/character in which they represent. None of the yarns belong to or are affiliated with any of the fandoms, franchises, or characters for which it is inspired from.

For information on the different bases available, please click here

Daenerys Targaryen pairs well with the following yarn:

Pure Silver

Lilacs In Bloom

Golden Treasure

blog.title: What Now
blog.description: Bunch of stuff about writing, books and fanfiction. Fandoms. and Supernatural. Like a lot of Supernatural. My AO3 My rewatch thread of all 14 seasons of Supernatural starts Here

body:
Okay so

I always thought Dany’s dragons represented her true inner feelings (she chained them while she had to make a lot of compromises she didn’t want to make, for example); and that the Direwolves were meant to represent the fate of their Stark.

But if that’s true, I’m super nervous about Sansa.

Like I could expand on that, but I’d be far more interested in hearing what ppl have to say…

summary: if dany were the mad, tyrannical queen that people say it would make the most sense for her to just....stay put. she doesn’t...
body: if dany were the mad, tyrannical queen that people say it would make the most sense for her to just….stay put. she doesn’t need to provide the northerners with dragonglass (and resources and men to mine it!!!) she could have just sat where she was and let the white walkers destroy the north (which she notes is in open rebellion) and then destroyed them with her dragons. but she doesn’t.

summary: Jonerys fans say jonsa fans uses jon snow tag everytime but they also do too? And blame them for hating daenerys and wanting her...
body:
Ship wars in GOT.

Jonerys fans say jonsa fans uses jon snow tag everytime but they also do too? And blame them for hating daenerys and wanting her to suffer,which ı agree with some parts,but “many"of them hating sansa and saying shitty things about her??

Yes ı admit ı was a jonsa shipper once and ı didnt like daenerys or ı wanted to but it doesnt matter anymore. Even if ı see there is a possibility for politic jon and daenerys did some bad choices in season 7,ı dont want to daenerys to lose everything for jon to be king. Because she did everything for to take back what she think belonged to her. With good advisors/rulers by her side ı believe she can be very good queen. And ı hope as a daensa shipper,jonsa and jonerys fans see that both women are survivor and amazing person and both of them deserve to be happy because they gone throught so much.🙏🏼

I am not against shipping jonerys/jonsa but we can still respect each other while having difference.🙃
